## Project Overview
This project was completed as part of the Digital Literacy course at VIT Bhopal University. The purpose of this project is to develop essential digital skills such as creating a professional online presence, using digital tools effectively, communicating professionally, and understanding cyber safety.

The project consists of five tasks, each focusing on a different aspect of digital literacy. All tasks are organized in this repository.

